{
  "stem": "10572.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After, after we got our [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] things organized and started to realize that, life had to go on-- and I felt that my father and my sister were economically on a-- on a basis where they could support each other, support themselves.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was determined now to get into the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The peculiar thing was that I went to a dive port in Evans and here were these harmless good citizens who looked at this guy who was legally still a German.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he wanted to get in the American army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what was wrong with this guy?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I couldn't explain it to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they told me that they had to have the FBI check me out first before they could accept me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had given up everything I had done up to this point.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I got a job through a friend of mine who said to me-- he knew the personnel manager at Sears Roebuck.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I got a job at Sears Roebuck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they knew that I was waiting to be called into the service.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But somehow, we got along beautifully.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one day, somebody came and shopped me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Willmark Shopping Service.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I must have had a particularly good day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I got rated so high, that I was called to the store manager, who told me that Sears Roebuck had plans for me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "After I came out of service, they wanted to put me into executive training.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I somehow felt kind of a happy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because I had heard that after the First World War people were selling apples.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And at least I had a chance to work with Sears.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was somehow kind of a come-down for me when, two weeks after this meeting with Mr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Simmons, I was called into personnel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was a new gal in personnel-- had a job to interrogate or interview people who had a shortage or an overage in their cash register.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I tried to explain it to this girl, that it was very simple and it happened often.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That because of the seven cash registers, there was overage or shortage of whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I had a shortage of $19.95.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And to make a long story short, she ultimately told me and threatened me that if I wouldn't sign the statement that I had been interviewed, then she had to turn it over to the store manager.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I told her to go ahead and turn it over to the store manager.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She didn't know that the store manager and I were on real good terms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And-- But in the meantime, I became interested in that girl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And ultimately, this cute little girl at personnel at Sears became my wife.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And she-- after I went into service, she went into service.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She went to the Coast Guard Academy in New London, Connecticut, and got her commission.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it was my particular tragedy that not only did she find that I had a shortage of my cash, but she also outranked me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was an enlisted man, and she was an officer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I figured, c'est la guerre or c'est la vie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So be it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then, I, I, I went into-- went into the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And after I was through with basic training on the 11th of November, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we had to pass the commanding general because of Armistice Day.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1942.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a bitter cold day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the winters in Virginia can be miserable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of these guys-- my buddies-- were cussing about this horrible cold winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they didn't know that it was the 11th of November that we were marching.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And five years earlier to the day, I arrived in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this time, I was marching with a gun on my shoulders, in American uniform, passing the American flag, the symbol of freedom and dignity for man.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was very happy without being able to explain to them why they shouldn't cuss.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my army career was, was a very, very interesting one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if I would have designed it myself, I couldn't have done a better job.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I finally ended up-- and I first was in a prisoner of war camp in Camp Ashby, Virginia, where we had 3,000 Afrika Korps prisoners in the camp who had been transferred from Camp Forrest, Tennessee, from another camp where they were running the camp.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now they came into Camp for-- through Camp Ashby.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, my commanding officer called me in and told me that three days after they arrived, that they had gone on strike.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he didn't know what to do with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
